twoColConflict-explainconflict:
Appears at the top of a page when there is an edit conflict.

Parameters:
$1 - Label of the save button. Either {{msg-mw|savechanges}} or {{msg-mw|publishchanges}}.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|Savearticle}}
twoColConflict-changes-col-title: Header for the unified diff column with the changes.
twoColConflict-changes-col-desc:
Description text for the unified diff column with the changes.

Parameters:
$1 - Username of the user that edited the current revision of the page.
$2 - User-formatted time and date when the current revision was changed.
$3 - User-formatted time and date of the conflicting change.
twoColConflict-editor-col-desc:
Description text for the editor column.

Parameters:
$1 - Username of user that edited the last valid version.
$2 - User-formatted time and date when the current revision was changed.
twoColConflict-diffchange-own-title: The title text in the unified diff view for changes by the user.
twoColConflict-diffchange-foreign-title:
The title text in the unified diff view for conflicting changes.

Parameters:
$1 - Username of the user that edited the current revision of the page.
